b'65 million years ago, a meteorite impact and millennia of collapsing limestone left a mysterious water world underneath the jungle of the Yucatan peninsula in Mexico. \xe2\x81\xa3

b'The @lafortunaatitlan is powered entirely by solar energy, built from bamboo, and filled with furniture carved by local Guatemalan artisans using trees harvested from the surrounding area.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
The husband and wife duo behind the hotel have combined their years of working in environmental protection and the tourist industry to create this unique paradise on the shores of Lake Atitlan.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Expect days of uninterrupted relaxation in one of five private bungalows, nestled in lush jungle with a view of Atitla\xcc\x81n\xe2\x80\x99s volcanic coastline. A must-do? The outdoor showers beneath the star-speckled night sky will make you fall in love with the world all over again. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3

b'Located in the tranquil area of Val di Sole, @chalet_al_foss offers some awesome panoramic views of the Presanella glacier and nearby mountains. Whether you\xe2\x80\x99re there in the summer or winter, the Italian Alps will beckon you to explore it all.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Framed by the magnificent Dolomites, lush valleys, and abundant orchards, there are so many inviting trails across a diversity of landscapes. And when you\xe2\x80\x99re done? Take a dip in the warmth of the rooftop pool. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3

b"Anyone who loves to relax and soak up the sights, sounds and smells of a wild beach, will find Salmon Beach a great choice for some nature appreciation - but don't expect to a swim here.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Just a few kilometres west of Windy Harbour, this rugged and unspoilt beach feels the full force of winds and swells sweeping up from the southern ocean. We\xe2\x80\x99d recommend this spot for chilling out, watching the crashing waves and clouds passing by. Plus if you\xe2\x80\x99re here towards the end of the day the sunsets can be beautifully moody too. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3

\xe2\x81\xa3

b"Bawah is a barefoot, back-to-nature haven, set in a marine conservation area across six lush, jungle-covered islands, three turquoise lagoons, and 13 beaches.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Located between Malaysia and Borneo, this private-island reserve prides itself not only on its beauty but its eco mindset. Locally-grown ingredients can be found on the Asian-fusion menu at their Tree Top restaurant - plus there's even a zero-waste program in place, no pesticides in sight, and a no-fishing rule. Bawah really does offer the true meaning of sustainable luxury. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @travelinghawks\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Bawah #Indonesia\xe2\x81\xa3"

b'In the district of El Darie\xcc\x81n you\xe2\x80\x99ll find the largest reservoir in Colombia and one of the largest in all of America: Lake Calima. Located just 86 kilometers from Cali, it sits surrounded by the most beautifully vibrant landscapes - but beauty isn\xe2\x80\x99t all that these waters offer\xe2\x80\xa6\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Among the many titles this lake holds is that of having one of the fastest winds in Latin America and the third in the world. Because of this, it\xe2\x80\x99s more than an ideal place for practicing water sports - especially if you like to do so with a scenic view. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3

\xe2\x81\xa3
#LagoCalima #Colombia \xe2\x81\xa3'

b'Parque Nacional del Manu is where endless shades of green, cascading waterfalls, and the tropical wildlife of the Amazon Rainforest meets the winding ridges and towering glaciers of the Andes. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Sprawling a gigantic area of 17,162.95 km2 the contrasting landscapes, together in one place, is something you have to see with your own eyes, and not something you\xe2\x80\x99ll ever forget. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @nainoalanger\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#ParqueNacional #Peru\xe2\x81\xa3'

b'Located in the heart of the Great Barrier Reef, on Whitsunday Island, is (arguably) Australia\xe2\x80\x99s most beautiful beach: Whitehaven.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
From the air, Whitehaven just doesn\xe2\x80\x99t look real. Its swirling sands, teal water, and sculpted channels twist and turn as if painted, forming a seriously breathtaking landscape. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
To protect the environment and beauty here, the beach and the surrounding areas are now national parks, so whatever your plans, be sure to pack plenty of food and water, as there are no restaurants or hotels\xe2\x80\xa6 just nature.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @thefreedomcomplex\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Whitehaven #WhitehavenBeach #WhitsundayIsland\xe2\x81\xa3'

b"Ecotourism is ever more important to ensure the protection of our oceans. @mooreamoanatours is a team of watermen, biologists, and photographers sharing their passion for the wildlife of Mo'orea. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3

b'Located inside one of Argentina\xe2\x80\x99s many national parks, surrounded by 67,720 hectares of Paranaense Jungle, the mystical Iguazu\xcc\x81 Falls is an explorer\xe2\x80\x99s dream. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Viewing them has been made easy by two circuit trails, and visitors are encouraged to try both to see the cascading water from different perspectives. Tip: beware the bottom trail - the force of the water falling creates a thick mist, and never fails to wet its audience. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3

b'The Islas Marietas, off the west coast, is home to one of the most unusual beaches you\xe2\x80\x99ll find - Mexico\xe2\x80\x99s \xe2\x80\x98Hidden Beach\xe2\x80\x99. A gaping hole in the surface of this lush green island opens up to a secret sandy cavern, with the blue waters of the Pacific rushing in.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Access is through a narrow tunnel from the ocean, which you\xe2\x80\x99ll need to swim through at low tide. While you may think this would put people off, there is actually the opposite problem - the beach is hidden, but no secret. To prevent damage to the fragile ecosystem here, only 100 people are permitted each day, so you\xe2\x80\x99ll need a pass to enter paradise. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @postandfly\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#PlayaDelAmor #IslasMarietas #Mexico\xe2\x81\xa3'

b'With twenty National Protected Areas covering more than 21% of the country, Laos is home to a diverse variety of nature and wildlife. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
The country is landlocked with no coastline but is known for its spectacular limestone mountains, and endless opportunities to explore the fairy-like forests and caves. Put on some sturdy shoes and climb the many slippery trails to discover these shallow turquoise pools. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3

b'At the foot of Cerro Polques in Bolivia, lies Termas de Polques, a small 29\xc2\xb0C hot-spring formed as a result of volcanic activity from the nearby volcano. Although the pool is by no means boiling, its mineral-rich waters are more than suitable for bathing. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
With pink flamingos feeding in the multicolored-lagunas nearby, alpacas wandering as they please, and mountain views all around, this has to be one of the most captivating and unique places on the planet. An experience any traveler should put to the top of their list. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @_romanmoran\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#TermasDePolques #Bolivia\xe2\x81\xa3'

b'Swimming with whale sharks is becoming an increasingly popular tourist activity around the world. Unfortunately, as more travellers seek this experience, sustainable and ethical practices are often bypassed to meet demand.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3

\xe2\x81\xa3
Whether you choose Oslob, Dumaguete, Donsol or one of the many other swim spots, do your research - there\xe2\x80\x99s no shortage of amazing responsible tourism opportunities to view marine life in the Philippines.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3

#Cebu #Philippines #whaleshark #underwaterworld #betterworld #bucketlist #exploremore #oceanlove'

b'There\xe2\x80\x99s no absence of beautiful lakes around the world. Some are dark, flat and act as giant mirrors reflecting their stunning sceneries, while others are turquoise and crystal clear all the way to the bottom. They all vary, but have you ever seen a lake that\xe2\x80\x99s not blue or green, but completely pink? \xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\xa0\x80\xe2\x81\xa3
Walvis Bay (vahl-fis bay) in Namibia produces 90% of the salt for sub-saharan Africa from huge salt flats. Microorganisms living here release a reddish pink substance as a part of their photosynthesis process, which tints these pools into beautiful deep pink lakes. A must-see phenomenon. \xe2\x81\xa3

b'\xe2\x80\x9cIt seems like every sunset, I\xe2\x80\x99m out in the water. I think the golden light has something big to do with the way I feel. I just want to stay in it.\xe2\x81\xa3

I can be so sensitive but it\xe2\x80\x99s magical when I relax into it - the water so silky, like a divine stillness. It blows my mind to feel the softness, it\xe2\x80\x99s a sensory overload and so quiet.\xe2\x80\x9d - @chessachasingwaves\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @paupauphoto\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#SouthSumatra #Indonesia #beachlife #surflife #surflove'

b'At the quiet-end of a 2km stretch of white sand, bordered by granite boulders, @ParadiseSunHotel offers charming, ocean facing French-Creole chalets, set within lush tropical gardens. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Follow the palm-fringed walkways down onto the shore where the turquoise horizon is interrupted only by the postcard beauty of St Pierre Island and a few bobbing sail boats. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
No shoes? No problem. It\xe2\x80\x99s all about barefoot relaxation at Paradise Sun.\xe2\x81\xa3

\xe2\x81\xa3

b'\xe2\x80\x98A picturesque sunrise along the reef was the perfect reward to an early morning wake up call. The crashing waves of the golden ocean were a stark contrast to the calmness of the blue lagoon. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Usually I like picking between warm or cool tones in a photo, but when they want to naturally meet in the middle, you won\xe2\x80\x99t hear me complain.\xe2\x80\x99 - @erubes1\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3

b'"My focus has always been sharks, they\xe2\x80\x99re the animals I grew up with. I never had an urge to fight for them though, until I started to see a decline in their numbers, even in my short lifetime.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Now, the most important thing I do for this species is something far too rare in conservation - I talk to the enemy. I started establishing relationships around the world with the groups of people who kill and hunt sharks for survival and recreation, and it\xe2\x80\x99s through these relationships that I\xe2\x80\x99ve seen the most change. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
I began @projecthiu, which offers an alternative income to shark fishermen through tourism. This prevents them from fishing sharks but still allows them to make the money they they need. Between enemy and friend I\xe2\x80\x99ve found the most effective way to work towards a better world." - @sharkgirlmadison\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#betterworld #underwaterworld #oceanlove'

b"Emerald elevation in the Mentawai Islands; the holy grail of endless surf breaks. As you're reading this, another perfect wave is going unridden...\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3

\xe2\x81\xa3

\xe2\x81\xa3
#Mentawai #Indonesia #bucketlist #beachlife #surfsup #surflife"
b'Sun down, spirits high. #ThisIsLiving'

b"Is there anything better than trading waves back and forth with a handful of your closest pals, in a remote and tropical location?\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
After the multiple connecting flights and the countless hours spent at airports, there's nothing more rewarding than the paddle out at a foreign surf spot and swinging into the first wave of the session \xe2\x80\x93 especially when your friends watch on. Here\xe2\x80\x99s @harrisonsan reaping the benefits of multiple days in transit. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3

b'Suspended among the trees on Tulum\xe2\x80\x99s dramatic coastline, @Azulik is more a part of nature than it is a hotel, and oozes rustic charm. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Connected by a maze of hand-crafted wooden walkways, the 48 villas are barely distinguishable from the jungle, and a unique wetland system runs under the hotel, nourishing the jungle floor and adding to the wild ambience. The perfect getaway, where nature, art, and ancestral wisdom coexist.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @lucaspinhel\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Tulum #Mexico #bucketlist #hiddentreasures #mindfulliving #inspiredbynature'

b'Swimming with whale sharks - an item often near the top of many traveller\xe2\x80\x99s bucket-lists. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Those fortunate enough to tick this off will know the inexplicable feeling associated with realising one of their dreams. These are the kind of experiences that have the power to take a trip from wonderful to unparalleled, and create memories that linger in the mind long after the trip has ended. Any opportunity to encounter these majestic creatures in their natural habitat is bound to be magical, and definitely worth going out of your way for. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Remember: keep a respectful distance from these gentle giants, and resist the urge to touch them or use flash photography.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @cherylalba\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Cebu #Philippines #underwaterworld #bucketlist #exploremore'

b'Other than 700 Balinese long-tailed monkeys, the Sacred Monkey Forest Sanctuary in Ubud is home to over 186 species of trees in 12.5 hectares of forest and three holy temples. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
You can spend hours wandering the nature reserve, interacting with the monkeys and in awe of the unearthly scenery. With giant roots twisted around huge stone statues and bridges dating back to around 1350, there\xe2\x80\x99s plenty to explore.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @tilehu95\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Ubud #Bali #bucketlist #exploremore'

b'Patillas, known as "La Esmeralda del Sur" (the emerald of the south), is where the lush green mountains meet the beaches, on the southeastern coast of Puerto Rico.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Those who prefer hiking and hidden watering holes will have plenty to explore around Carite State Forest, as well as the many orange and sugar cane plantations. But if you're looking to kick back on a tranquil beach for the day, there are several just off the scenic PR-3 road.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3

\xe2\x81\xa3

b'While violence has dominated international headlines for El Salvador, and keeps many travellers at bay, the vast majority of this beautiful country remains untouched by its \xe2\x80\x98troubles\xe2\x80\x99, just waiting to be explored. \xe2\x81\xa3 \xe2\x81\xa3
Those who do visit are pleasantly surprised by the warm welcome they receive and by just how much this small country has to offer. World-class surfing on empty, dark-sand beaches, coffee plantations, a number of volcanoes and sublime national parks are just some of the things you can experience. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @joellefriend\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#ElSalvador #bucketlist #exploremore'

b'No surf bucket list is complete without a trip to the Mentawai Islands. Situated 150km off the coast of Sumatra in the Indian Ocean, the Mentawais are home to many desolate palm-covered islands and some of the best surf spots in the world.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
You can kick-it in luxury at a land-based surf camp with all the comforts of home. Or, take to the high-seas by jumping on a surf charter, giving you the freedom to move easily between the many islands and reefs on offer \xe2\x80\x93 nothing beats surfing different breaks and waking to a different view through your porthole each morning. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @johnnyjungle\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Mentawai #Indonesia #bucketlist #beachlife #surfsup #surflife'

b'We\xe2\x80\x99re pretty sure this is what heaven looks like\xe2\x80\xa6 @Kamandalu enchants guests by capturing the essence of a traditional Balinese village, incorporating luxury into its natural landscape. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Take in the stunning views across the valley of Ubud and the Petanu River while enjoying a daily yoga session, or venture out to explore the productive rice terraces and mature coconut palms. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3

\xe2\x81\xa3
#Ubud #Bali #Indonesia #bucketlist #hiddentreasures'

b"Hands down the most famous and infamous peak on the planet, Hawaii\xe2\x80\x99s Pipeline is the benchmark by which all other waves are measured. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3

\xe2\x81\xa3

\xe2\x81\xa3

b'Imagine waking up to the sounds of birds and monkeys in the nearby jungle and this view. Eden on the Chocolata is an eco-lodge built to give you the experience of being close to nature, but with the warm embrace of comfort and hospitality. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Enjoy the ocean view over Nacascolo Bay from the yoga deck, cool off in the pool from the year-round sun in Nicaragua or exercise on the outdoor fitness trail. Eden inspires you to be active and adventurous as well as meditate and relax. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3

b"It's hard to resist the powder-fine sand and clear turquoise waters of Jervis Bay, on the south coast of New South Wales. Leaping dolphins and migrating whales (May to November) add to its appeal, and there's plenty of opportunity for diving, snorkelling or kayaking.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
You can try your luck spotting whales from the shore, as they sometimes swim into the bay with their young, but your best bet is exploring the ocean and many sea caves, waiting for these gentle giants to approach. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3

b'On St. Lucia\xe2\x80\x99s west coast just outside Soufri\xc3\xa8re, @Stonefieldvillaresort is more than a tropical island resort. \xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3

b'Situated on a quiet hilltop in the spectacular Sapa valley of northern Vietnam, the @topasecolodge is unrivalled in location. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
It\xe2\x80\x99s a 45 minute scenic bus ride from Sapa town (you\xe2\x80\x99ll probably encounter a few buffalos, cows and goats along the way), offering a very remote wifi-free welcome. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Our tip: when you\xe2\x80\x99re done relaxing it the infitity pool, visit the five different hill-tribes to experience hidden trails, breathtaking scenery and the fascinating local culture of these mountainous people.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3

\xe2\x81\xa3

\xe2\x81\xa3

b'We all need a sanctuary to relax and reset. @Mandla_nicaragua retreat in Nicaragua offers a place to come for privacy and to enjoy all the adventures this beautiful country has to offer.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Located in a small bay with one of the most consistent surf breaks, \xe2\x80\x98Pistols\xe2\x80\x99 is great for experienced surfers and right on your doorstep. For those looking for something a little more forgiving, a short 5 minute walk South of Mandla offers fantastic beginner waves. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3

b'\xe2\x80\x98Patagonia has drawn people to its beauty for decades and it\xe2\x80\x99s easy to see why with views like this.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
I hired a taxi from the nearby town of Puerto Natales and set out to meet up with the rest of my group. The taxi driver didn\xe2\x80\x99t speak a word of English, but it didn\xe2\x80\x99t matter. We were both in awe of the beautiful scenery around us and the universal word \xe2\x80\x9cwhoa\xe2\x80\x9c was understood.\xe2\x80\x99 - @thismattexists\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3

b'\xe2\x80\x98I draw on the sand with whatever is to hand, sometimes pieces of wood found along the shore, sometimes I use a rake. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
The pieces I create are all forms of ephemeral art - they\xe2\x80\x99re not permanent. Beaches offer a beautifully big space, so I draw on wet sand at low tide, and each day nature rubs away my art and gives me a brand new canvas.\xe2\x80\x99 - @jbenart\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#France #beachlife #inspiredbynature'

b'Tucked away in the dramatic cliffs of the Amalfi Coast, @villatreville is a charming cluster of villas boasting unparalleled views of Positano and a whole lot of character. \xe2\x81\xa3

Explore the gardens, terraces and balconies wrapped in lush vines of bougainvillea, or head down to the private beach to recline in Mediterranean sunshine. A true Italian paradise with the atmosphere of a private home.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3

\xe2\x81\xa3

\xe2\x81\xa3
You should come here if you want to: see its unique design, take some amazing sunset shots or just enjoy a beer with uninterrupted views of the Indian Ocean and sound of lapping waves. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3

#Jimbaran #Bali #bucketlist #sunsetlovers'

b'Pula\xe2\x80\x99s beautifully rugged coastline offers much to be discovered, but if it\xe2\x80\x99s unspoiled you\xe2\x80\x99re looking for, Veli Brijun is a must. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Catch the ferry from just outside Pula to visit this secluded and uninhabited island. Animals roam free in its parkland, so look out for peacocks, as well as dinosaur footprints (it\xe2\x80\x99s an ancient site). You can also visit the remains of Roman villas or head to the cliffs to take in the sunset, and catch a glimpse of dolphins offshore. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3

b'Swaying palms, tropical forests and beaches beyond belief, the Seychelles is a real-life paradise. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Staying at @BanyanTree_Seychelles you\xe2\x80\x99ll enjoy the unspoiled beauty of the islands and an infinity pool that stretches out to the ocean, the invisible edge making for a memorable swimming experience. Beyond the main hub, the villas dot the beach and climb the hillside behind - the perfect hideaway.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @pierreschuester\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Seychelles #BucketList #HiddenTreasures #BeachLife'

b'Located on the shore of Echo Beach, one of the most well known beaches in Bali, @LaBrisaBali welcomes you with breathtaking d\xc3\xa9cor and genuine Balinese hospitality.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Built with reclaimed wood from more than 500 fishing boats and serving up a whole lotta seafood and local produce, La Brisa is devoted to being sustainably sourced. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Stop by and take in this enchanting yet soothing atmosphere, it will be well worth it.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @thoughtsofping\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Canggu #BaliIndonesia #BucketList #BeachLife #ChillTime'
location_name: b'La Brisa, Echo Beach, Canggu, Bali'

caption:
b'This tree is the only living thing in The Dead Sea - and the lowest tree on earth, at 1424 feet below sea level. \xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
The Dead Sea offers no signs of life below the surface due to its searingly high salt concentration (it\xe2\x80\x99s almost 10 times saltier than the ocean) but has become a popular spot for travellers.\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
Located between Ein Bokek and Neve Zohar, Israel, you can see the tree for yourself and float on the surface of these alien-like waters. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @madetwotravel\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
#TheDeadSea #EinBokek #BucketList'

b"\xe2\x80\x985 years ago I remember being knocked out in a yoga class in Bali. I felt awkward doing the poses and figured it just wasn't for me.\xe2\x81\xa3 But now, here I am.\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3Last year, I made a decision to lean into my discomforts. Yoga makes me uncomfortable because it challenges me to be present, so I didn't enjoy the thought of spending 30 minutes or more intensely focusing on bending my body into weird shapes.\xe2\x81\xa3 But I also knew that's why I needed to do it.\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3If you know it's good for your mind and your body, but it makes you feel uncomfortable, embrace that discomfort. Face it and challenge yourself to rise above it.\xe2\x80\x99\xe2\x81\xa3 - @heyashleyrenne\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#ThisIsLiving #India #YogaLove #SelfCare"

b'Indonesia is a haven for surfers all over the world, and Krui is the capital of the West Coast, Lampung. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
This winding coastline offers white sandy beaches stretching for miles and over a dozen world class waves to take on. On the outskirts of Krui, you\xe2\x80\x99ll find a cluster of surf camps, where you can reward yourself with some relaxation after a day out on the ocean.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Note: The waves here are mostly suited for intermediate to advanced surfers. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @chessachasingwaves @paupauphoto\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Sumatra #Indonesia #SurfsUp #SurfLife #BeachLife'

b'Located near the little fishing village of El Transito, on the coast between Le\xc3\xb3n and Managua, @nimbu_surfhouse is a place where travellers come together. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
This eco-friendly lodge is a place for good vibes and conversations, where you can enjoy surfing, yoga, swimming and local food. And if you prefer to just chill? Grab a cold drink from the bar, hang in a hammock and enjoy the breathtaking sunsets. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @nimbu_surfhouse\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#BeachLife #SunsetLovers #HiddenTreasures #SurfsUp #YogaLove #SelfCare'

b"\xe2\x80\x98Just a small collection of plastic fragments washed ashore with the waves, on the beaches here in Hawaii. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
It\xe2\x80\x99s these plastics and microplastic pieces, that are increasingly smaller, that are ingested by marine animals, putting them at serious risk and polluting our oceans and beaches.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Let's become aware of our littering and make a habit of collecting trash in the places we love. It\xe2\x80\x99s not a solution but a grain of sand in a big problem we face today.\xe2\x80\x99 - @catalinahotz\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#BetterWorld #OceanLove #PlasticFreeLiving"

b"\xe2\x80\x98Just a small collection of plastic fragments washed ashore with the waves, on the beaches here in Hawaii. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
It\xe2\x80\x99s these plastics and microplastic pieces, that are increasingly smaller, that are ingested by marine animals, putting them at serious risk and polluting our oceans and beaches.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Let's become aware of our littering and make a habit of collecting trash in the places we love. It\xe2\x80\x99s not a solution but a grain of sand in a big problem we face today.\xe2\x80\x99 - @catalinahotz\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#BetterWorld #OceanLove #PlasticFreeLiving"

b"Located just off of Norman\xe2\x80\x99s Cay, a quiet little island in the Exumas, lies a corroding reminder of paradise's brief but sinister past.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
A plane once used for drug trafficking in the 1970\xe2\x80\x99s, is now an excellent dive spot in warm shallow waters, less than 10 feet from the surface. Adding to the appeal of the crash site, many species of fish and coral have built their habitats around the wreck.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
A must-see for adventurers wanting to immerse themselves in the history and natural beauty of The Bahamas. \xe2\x81\xa3#ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @celiasmith\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Bahamas #UnderwaterWorld #ExploreMore #OceanLove"
b'Take a sandy seat more often. #ThisIsLiving'

b'While The Bahamas offer everything recreational divers can wish for, one experience is on most diver\xe2\x80\x99s list: shark diving. Shark populations in this part of the Caribbean are thriving and The Bahamas offer some of the best shark dives in the world. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Take the plunge into the deep blue waters of Nassau, where encountering lemon sharks, Caribbean reef sharks and blacktips are guaranteed but that\xe2\x80\x99s not the end of the list\xe2\x80\xa6\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @sabinebanet @andremusgrove\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Nassau #Bahamas #ThisIsLiving #UnderwaterWorld #ExploreMore #OceanLove'

b'Pamukkale (meaning cotton castle in Turkish) has been made world famous by the gleaming white travertine terraces overrunning with warm, mineral-rich waters on the mountain. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Above the terraced basins lies Hierapolis, once a Roman spa city, which now has considerable ruins to be explored. A Marvel of Nature and a great historical site, side by side - one to add to your bucket list for sure.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @expeditionearth.live\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Pamukkale #Turkey #BucketList #ExploreMore'

b"Located in the center of Polignano a Mare, @RistoranteGrottaPalazzese was carved out of the cliff\xe2\x80\x99s limestone by the sea, and has hosted elegant dinners since the 18th century.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Considered among the most enchanting outdoor restaurants in the world, visitors can dine suspended between the town above and the Adriatic Sea 74 feet below. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Tip: the dramatic view of lapping waves is best observed from one of the dimly-lit tables for two that sweep along the cave's edge.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @pinkines\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Italy #BucketList #HiddenTreasures"

b'Taking inspiration from Hindu and Tibetan Buddhist imagery, Cape Town artist Daniel Popper is known globally for his larger-than-life sculptures, and spectacular public art installations.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Travelling to Queensland, Australia he has created a five meter high wooden female deity, depicted rising from the earth, welcoming viewers and embracing the beauty of her surroundings. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Visit the sculpture after dark to view her all-encompassing glowing aura.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera::@danielpopper\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Queensland #Austrailia #InspiredByNature #BeachLife'
b'Living on a warm breeze and ocean spray. #ThisIsLiving'

b'Stimulate your body and mind, by searching for new and unexplored places. Nestled within 400 acres of jungle, along the shore of the Rio Dulce, the @HaciendaTijax offers a laid-back retreat, well suited to spiritual pursuits. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Relax and become closer to nature or reward yourself with adventure walking the miles of trails and natural water springs Guatemala offers. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @sofia_elena96\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Guatemala #ExploreMore #HiddenTreasures #YogaLove #SelfCare'
location_name: b'Hacienda Tijax Jungle Ecolodge (Rio Dulce Hotel)'

caption:
b"Many travellers love to experience the beauty of coral reefs up close, and visitors to The Blue Bay Marine Park, Mauritius, are no exception. The bay boasts beautiful coral gardens with a remarkable surface area and biodiversity, but today it's under threat as a result of urbanisation and tourism. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
There is an imminent need for more sustainable recreational snorkelling and diving, to protect these fragile ecosystems and the marine life that call them home. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @nicolesenn\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Mauritius #UnderwaterWorld #BetterWorld"

b'This eco-resort in Mexico has magical architecture and a jaw-dropping art museum. @sferik.art, located just 30mins from Tulum in the town of Francisco Uh May, is a free museum allowing entry to visitors willing to walk barefoot. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Comprising exhibitions of the world\xe2\x80\x99s finest visual artists, nature is at the heart of every project, creating a space of meditation and urging visitors to think about the future of our oceans, jungles and forests. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @ionexplorer\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Tulum #Mexico #InspiredByNature #BetterWorld #MindfulLiving #Meditation'

b'Nestled on the shore of Seminyak beach, sits @LaPlanchaBali (pronounced ah-la-plahn-chah), a colourful and vibrant beach shack offering a fusion of two cultures, Balinese and Spanish. \xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
You\xe2\x80\x99ll be welcomed by the Chiringuito style, mouth watering tapas and drinks,  whilst taking in the natural beauty of Bali.\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
Opt for the brightly coloured beanbags and Balinese umbrellas on the sand, grab a corona and enjoy one of the best sunset spots in Bali. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @sataychick\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
#Seminyak #BaliBeach #BucketList #BeachLife'

b'Although not far from the bustling city of Jerusalem, you\xe2\x80\x99ll feel worlds away, surrounded by nature at Ein Gedi.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
One of the most beautiful places in Israel, this nature reserve offers spectacular landscapes, botanical gardens and over nine different hiking trails - ranging from just half an hour in length, to a full day.\xe2\x81\xa3 Whichever trail you take, you can expect breathtaking scenic views of both the desert and the Dead Sea. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @madetwotravel\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#EinGedi #Israel #BucketList #ExploreMore'

b'Described as a \xe2\x80\x98desert theme park\xe2\x80\x99, Merzouga is a calm and quiet town rich in culture and full of activities. Relax in the oasis of your Moroccan riad or venture out to walk the tops of the Sahara dunes and tour the Dayet Srji (a seasonal salt lake famous for its array of migratory birds).\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Tip: visit between September and November, when the weather isn\xe2\x80\x99t too hot and sandstorms aren\xe2\x80\x99t as likely. #ThisIsLiving \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera::@kerinanewell
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Merzouga #Morocco #BucketList #ExploreMore'
b'Living the only way we know how; in surroundings that lift our soul. #ThisIsLiving'

b'A historic gem by the sea, @Cap_Rocat is an ancient fortress located in the most secluded area of the Bay of Palma, Mallorca. With the spa carved out of the depths of the rocks, 12 meters below ground, it\xe2\x80\x99s the most sheltered nook of the fortress to enjoy a sensory journey and a moment of pure disconnection.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Need some next-level relaxation? Indulge in their Hammam Ritual experience, finishing off with a dip in the indoor seawater pool, naturally lit with views of blue skies. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @jeremyaustiin\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Mallorca #BucketList #HiddenTreasures #PeaceofMind #SelfCare'

b'One mile off the coast, perched on stilts amongst the waves of Parottee Bay, you\xe2\x80\x99ll find Floyd\xe2\x80\x99s @official_pelican_bar. Known as one of the best beach bars in the world, it\xe2\x80\x99s not just a hut made from scrap wood, it\xe2\x80\x99s the perfect way to spend a day.\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
Enjoy beer, seafood and sunbathing after arriving by boat (the only way you can get here), or join the locals playing dominos, and taking ocean dips between drinks.\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
Whether you\xe2\x80\x99re staying in Negril, Ocho Rios, or Montego Bay, it\xe2\x80\x99s definitely worth the trip. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @annesha.adams\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
#Jamaica #BucketList #ChillTime #BeachLife'

b'The search for paradise appears to be over, and you\xe2\x80\x99ll find it at the @Hurawalhi resort, in the pristine northern Lhaviyani Atoll. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
The resort\xe2\x80\x99s spectacular 5.8 Undersea Restaurant (named after its location - 5.8 meters beneath the lagoon) is a whole other experience, being the world\xe2\x80\x99s largest all-glass undersea restaurant. Diners are seated at one of only ten tables and can enjoy an intimate dining experience with beautiful panoramic views of the ocean and the marine life that call it home. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @jeremyaustiin\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Maldives #BucketList #UnderwaterWorld #HiddenTreasures'

b'The natural beauty in Eastern Indonesia is infinite, and the island of Wangi-Wangi is no exception. It\xe2\x80\x99s a well known spot among divers from all over the world, for its diversity in underwater species, but there\xe2\x80\x99s a treasure onshore that shouldn\xe2\x80\x99t be missed.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
To the northwest of the island you\xe2\x80\x99ll find Wasabinua Resto & Coffee, a cafe built on a small coral island, with stunning ocean views and a relaxed atmosphere. This place is perfectly located for watching the sunset and a must-see when visiting Wangi-Wangi.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @joeadimara_\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#WangiWangi #Indonesia #BucketList #BeachLife #ChillTime'

b'This alien world is about the hottest place on Earth. The Danakil Depression in northern Ethiopia, a moon-like landscape that stays without rain for most of the year, is one of the most fascinating environments in the world.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
If you\xe2\x80\x99re looking for extreme adventure, few corners of the globe can match this overwhelming wilderness. Travel here to see the wonders of sulfur hot springs, volcanoes, acidic pools, and bathe in colourful mineral-laden lakes formed above tectonic plates. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @ianharper\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Ethiopia #BucketList #ExploreMore'

b'Immerse yourself in the traditional fishing culture and history of Cam Thanh Village (often called the Coconut Village), all from the comfort, and a little instability, of a bamboo basket boat.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
After boarding at the river bank, a local guide will take you on an hour long ride down the Cua Dai River, meandering through the maze-like network of channels, canals, and coconut palms - the best way to experience this part of Vietnam. #ThisisLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @johan_drone_adventures\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Vietnam #BucketList #ExploreMore'

b'Can you imagine anything better than being surrounded by miles of turquoise ocean and postcard-perfect views whilst sipping on a cold beer? We can\xe2\x80\x99t.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
@cloud9_fiji is a two-level floating lounge in the middle of the South Pacific with a fully stocked bar, it\xe2\x80\x99s own wood-fired pizzeria and only a 40 minute boat ride from Port Denarau, Fiji. A must-visit spot. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @jeremyaustiin\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Fiji #BucketList #BeachLife #ChillTime'
b'Sand, smiles & a frothy lime. #ThisIsLiving'

b'Embracing both the forest and ocean, @LaLagunaBali is the definition of shabby-island-chic and a beautiful escape from the hustle and bustle of Bali. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
With tonnes of indoor and outdoor seating areas dotted with oversized cushions and mismatched, antique furniture, you\xe2\x80\x99ll want to lounge here for more than a few hours, dipping in and out of their great food and drink offering.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
When you arrive in Canggu, head to the beach. Halfway between Batu Belig and Berawa Beach is a huge wooden bridge, ready to transport you to this eclectic beach bar.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @melibelushi\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Bali #BeachLife #ChillTime #Disconnect'

b'Huacachina may be the most unexpected desert oasis. Found in southwestern Peru and known as the \xe2\x80\x98Oasis of America\xe2\x80\x99, it\xe2\x80\x99s one of the only true desert oases in the Americas. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Circled by palm trees, this remote village sits in a vast sea of sand, with its green lagoon waters at its center. Although it has a permanent population of less than 200, it\xe2\x80\x99s become a hub for travellers, drawn by the sport of sand-boarding on the dunes that reach several hundred feet high.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @liang.dennis\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Huacachina #Peru #BucketList #HiddenTreasures'

b'A meeting of jungle and beach, the @papayaplayaproject is an eco-friendly paradise along the Mexican Caribbean coast, cocooned by foliage. With huts beautifully designed to not interfere with nature, enjoy a new form of hospitality that merges the need to relax with local culture and sustainability.\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Tip: unwind and reconnect with an oceanfront Vinyasa yoga session, followed by their temazcal (a traditional Mayan steam bath). #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @expeditionearth.live\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Tulum #BucketList #HiddenTreasures #MindfulLiving #SelfCare #YogaLove'

b'Under the surface of Egypt\xe2\x80\x99s Red Sea, an underwater museum is fast becoming a divers haven. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
A community of professional divers, @i_dive_tribe, have installed environmentally-friendly statues on the seabed, designed to promote the growth of new coral and protect existing coral. By adding these diving attractions, it lessens the pressure on other exhausted reefs, giving them a chance to recover and regenerate. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @apneacarlos\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#Egypt #RedSea #UnderwaterWorld #OceanLove #BetterWorld'

b"La Fortuna de San Carlos is at the centre of many geological wonders, but hidden under a jungle canopy is a thermal river, warmed by Costa Rica's most active volcano. Take a dip or explore the surroundings of the Arenal Volcano, routinely bursting with lava, whilst the nearby Catarata de La Fortuna Waterfall gushes from 70 meters high. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @expeditionearth.live\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
#CostaRica #BucketList #ExploreMore"

b'The \xe2\x80\x98Big Island\xe2\x80\x99 is the largest Island in the United States and home to some of the most spectacular sights\xe2\x80\xa6 But tucked away in a jungle of exotic trees, is the cosiest treehouse only your childhood dreams could imagine. \xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
Watch the sunrise at breakfast, fall asleep counting stars (you can actually see Milky Way from your bed at night) and be sure to visit the Volcano National Park - it\xe2\x80\x99s only 15 minutes away! #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @lumadeline\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
#Hawaii #HiddenTreasures #ChillTime'

b'Surrounded by the tropical foliage of Thailand\xe2\x80\x99s ancient rainforest sits @discoversoneva, a hidden resort on the unspoiled island of Koh Kood. \xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
While you\xe2\x80\x99ll be in awe of the white-sand beaches and marine life, there\xe2\x80\x99s plenty deeper inland to keep you dreaming. Experience the ultimate dining experience, comfortably seated in a bamboo treepod meters off the ground. A whole new meaning to \xe2\x80\x98High Tea\xe2\x80\x99. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @travel_a_little_luxe\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
#Thailand #BucketList #ExploreMore #ChillTime'

b"The Devil's Cauldron (or \xe2\x80\x98El Pailon Del Diablo\xe2\x80\x99) is not for the faint-hearted. In the western foothills of the Ecuadorian Andes, these triple falls reward hikers with an intimate glimpse of one of the most powerful forces of nature, from heights of over 100 meters.\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
For those willing to get wet, a small cave trail follows the cliffs uphill through a series of narrow openings. When you\xe2\x80\x99re done, head down to the small restaurant at the bottom of the falls to dry off by the fireplace and enjoy very reasonably priced beers. #ThisIsLiving\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera:: @tysontravel\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
#Ecuador #Waterfall #BucketList #ExploreMore"
location_name: b'Cascada El Pail\xc3\xb3n Del Diablo, Ecuador'

caption:
b'Coral reefs are the rainforests of the ocean, they provide a home to so many beautiful underwater species, and the ocean provides a home for us. \xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
Overtime damage from both natural disaster and human activity has changed what were once vibrant reefs, into damaged remnants. Thankfully, projects like the @coralgardeners ensure these delicate ecosystems have the chance to thrive again. Each coral fragment collected is glued onto bamboo and brought to one of their nursery tables to grow. \xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
:camera::@ryan_borne\xe2\x81\xa3\xe2\x81\xa3
